# Routing Structure

The application uses React Router v6 for navigation. All routes are defined in [src/App.tsx](mdc:src/App.tsx).

## Main Routes
- `/` - Landing page
- `/about` - About page
- `/team` - Team page
- `/services` - Services page
- `/expertise` - Expertise page
- `/how-it-works` - How it works page

## User Service Routes
- `/start` - Service selection
- `/bulk-appraisal` - Bulk appraisal page
- `/bulk-appraisal/upload` - Bulk upload page
- `/bulk-appraisal/review` - Bulk review page
- `/report/:sessionId` - Report page
- `/submission-success` - Submission success page

## Authentication Routes
- `/login` - Login page
- `/signup` - Signup page
- `/reset-password` - Reset password page
- `/auth/success` - Auth success page

## Protected Routes
- `/dashboard` - User dashboard (requires authentication)
- `/profile` - User profile (requires authentication)

## Legal Routes
- `/terms` - Terms of service
- `/privacy` - Privacy policy
